{"title":"我认识的一个锻工","authors":["邓泽良"],"dates":[{"year":1984,"month":12,"day":17}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"我认识的一个锻工"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"邓泽良"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他并不象诗里写的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那么爽朗、粗犷；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他的性格是静，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"静得刚好和铿锵的锤音，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成为默契的一对。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他说话的声音，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就象淬火时"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢的一声“滋——”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"声音不高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然后是坚定的沉静。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}